 military forces, terrorists in South Asia, Iran&#x2019;s material support for proxy militants in the Middle East, violence in Venezuela, and the impact of tariffs on the Chinese economy."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"A key part of CIA analysis involves assessing foreign leaders. President Trump and other U.S. policymakers benefit by the CIA examining Kim&#x2019;s leadership style."}},{"is":"pull-quote","props":{"text":"The North Korean dictator has carried out ruthless internal purges of his government’s inner circle as well as executions of his own family members – including his half-brother Kim Jong Nam in Malaysia in 2017.","credit":""}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"What might CIA leadership analysts be writing about Kim Jong Un?"}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"The North Korean dictator has carried out ruthless internal purges of his government&#x2019;s inner circle as well as executions of his own family members &#x2013; including his half-brother Kim Jong Nam in Malaysia in 2017."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"At the same time, Kim Jong Un is a savvy operator who has demonstrated a high level of interpersonal skills when engaging with foreign leaders including President Trump, Chinese President Xi Jinping and South Korean President Moon Jae-in."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"In 2013 Kim announced North Korea would simultaneously build its nuclear capability and develop its economy. Then in 2018 he shifted course and said North Korea would focus on economic development because it had met its nuclear weapons goals."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Kim appears to be a rational actor who likely scripted these announcements to push his nuclear program to an advanced stage &#x2013; even at the risk of incurring economic sanctions on his country &#x2013; before swiveling to a policy of rapprochement designed to bring some sanctions relief."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Kim has proven that he is a shrewd tactician capable of skillfully moving his pieces on the chessboard."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"At the height of international tensions following repeated nuclear and ballistic missile tests in 2017, Kim used the 2018 Winter Olympics in South Korea as an opening gambit towards d&#xE9;tente with South Korea and the U.S."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"During the closing ceremonies for the Olympics, Kim&#x2019;s trusted former Chief of Intelligence Kim Yong Chol indicated North Korea&#x2019;s willingness to engage with the U.S."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Like his grandfather Kim Il Sung, who ruled before him, Kim Jong Un also has a predilection for grand and ambitious policy initiatives."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"At the April Inter-Korean summit, Kim became the first North Korean leader to enter South Korea since the Korean War ended in 1953. He conducted the first meeting by a North Korean leader with a sitting U.S president when he met with President Trump at the Singapore Summit in June."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"CIA leadership analysts undoubtedly have scoured all sources for information on Kim&#x2019;s early life and health, with an eye towards rounding out his psychological profile."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"As a child, Kim attended school in Switzerland. A shy student, he was known for being a basketball fan. Some reports have said that Kim, a heavy cigarette smoker who is significantly overweight, is a diabetic."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"Kim has an affinity for expensive alcohol and electronics. He built a new water park, an amusement park and a horseback riding club. Kim also built a sprawling luxury ski resort, complete with video screens playing government propaganda."}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"How might a leadership profile inform a denuclearization negotiations strategy to deal with Kim?"}},{"is":"paragraph","props":{"text":"CIA leadership analysts undoubtedly have sought to determine w